  <h1>I live up in the air and i don't belong to any country</h1>
  <p><em>May 13, 2025</em></p>
  <p>Stillness isn’t silence. It’s a hum. A low, aching presence that asks nothing from you but your breath.</p>
  <p>It’s the absence of reaction, not the absence of emotion. Stillness listens. Stillness witnesses.</p>
